[I] A helper library for file saving with confirmation dialogs used in gedit

[T] libgedit-gfls provides GNOME-style file-saving logic with confirmation
[T] dialogs and overwrite prompts, used by gedit and related text editors.

[U] https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/gedit/libgedit-gfls

